    "This modeling capability allows for rapid optimization of product profiles and reduces reliance on labor-intensive trial-and-error methods.",
    "In particular, the beverage industry has seen notable benefits from these approaches, as AI helps tailor flavor designs to evolving consumer preferences.",
    "Furthermore, both olfactory and gustatory domains utilize AI to enhance consumer insight through predictive analytics.",
    "By employing algorithms such as collaborative filtering and supervised learning, companies can analyze consumer data to identify preference trends, thereby informing targeted product development and marketing strategies.",
    "These techniques allow brands to tailor their offerings to diverse consumer segments and adapt more effectively to dynamic market demands."
